These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, asparagus
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, handball
City: rome, miami
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, emerald
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Food      | asparagus      | pomegranate    |
| Sport           | handball | skateboarding |
| City   | rome       | miami  |
| Color     | white      | emerald     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, australian
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, october
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
2. the australian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fisherman is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality          | australian | indian |
| Beverage   | sprite       | milk         |
| Birthday           | october     | march         |
| Job     | fisherman    | dressmaker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different games are played: whist, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, polish
House: craftsman, art-deco
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar
1. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Game         | chess          | whist |
| Nationality           | polish | japanese     |
| House   | craftsman            | art-deco         |
| Cigar     | bolivar         | pall-mall   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, board-games
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, october
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the dancer##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Hobby      | board-games     | reading   |
| Birthday   | october    | july |
| Flower   | marigold   | lily |
| Job           | dancer | freelancer    |

