.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, hamster
House: farmhouse, cottage
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, board-games
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, aristoff
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Pet      | hamster     | snake |
| House          | cottage   | farmhouse |
| Hobby   | board-games     | cooking     |
| Cigar     | cain | aristoff     |

 